extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: Huh...\. those statues seem familiar.\. Didn't expect to see those around here.
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Heu...\. ces statues me semblent familières.\. Je ne m'attendais pas à voir ça par ici.

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: Well...\. those faces sure are a landmark I suppose.
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Bon...\. ces visages sont certainement un point de repère, j'imagine.

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: Man, they really went full out with the jumping puzzles, didn't they?
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Oh Junge, ils ont vraiment mis le paquet sur les puzzles de saut, pas vrai ?

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: It just!\. Won't!\. Stop!
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Ça !\. Ne !\. S'arrêtera !\. Jamais !

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: More...\. stone...\. hopping...
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: On saute...\. encore...\. sur des rochers...

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: Japp, it surely would suck to miss a jump now.
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Japp, ce serait vraiment dommage de rater un saut là.

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: Better not slip now...
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Il faut mieux ne pas glisser là...

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: A checkpoint...\. Is this end of this jumping trail or have the Ancients planned more for us?
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Un point d'étape...\. Est-ce que c'est la fin de ce tracé de saut ou est-ce que les Anciens en ont prévu d'autres ?

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: Another Checkpoint!\. So...\. we're still not there yet?\. Or is that it?
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Encore un point de contrôle !\. Donc...\. on y est toujours pas ?\. Ou alors c'est fini ?

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: Another checkpoint?\. This...\. This is not it, isn't it?
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Encore une étape ?\. C'est...\. c'est pas fini, pas vrai ?

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: It seems like this might be it...\. but it probably isn't over yet.
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: On dirait qu'on atteint le bout...\. mais on y est pas encore.

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: IT'S STILL NOT OVER YOU GOT TO BE KIDDING ME!!
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: C'EST TOUJOURS PAS FINI !! C'EST UNE BLAGUE C'EST PAS POSSIBLE !!

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: It...\. still goes on.
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Et...\. ça continue...

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: Indeed, it looks the Ancients still have more plans for us.
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Il semblerait que les Anciens nous ont encore prévus d'autre chose.

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: I was right again...\. why do I have to be right again?!
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Et j'ai encore raison...\. Pourquoi il a fallu que j'aie encore raison ?!

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: Whohooo~!
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Youhouuu~ !

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: Look at her go!
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Regarde comment elle va !

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: Man, I wish they'd finally implement a proper swimming feature.
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Rah, si seulement ils avaient implémenté la fonctionnalité de pouvoir vraiment nager.

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: This place is the best!
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: C'est le paradis ici ! le paradis !

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: en_US
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: fr_FR

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: en_US
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: fr_FR

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: en_US
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: fr_FR

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: en_US
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: fr_FR

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: Of, this is a pleasant spot!\. I like those pink...\. tree things.
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Oui, c'est un endroit sympa !\. J'aime bien ces...\. machin arbres roses.

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: I also appreciate that there's no weird creatures nearby for once...
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: J'apprécie aussi qu'il n'y ait pas de créatures étranges au alentours, pour une fois...

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: We've been jumping along this way for quite a while now, haven't we?
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: On a sauté sur ce chemin depuis un bail maintenant, pas vrai ?

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: One developer sure must have been feeling ambitious when creating this jumping track...
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Un développeur à du se sentir ambitieux lorsqu'il a créé ce tracé de saut...

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: It seems this jumping puzzle might be on quite another level, indeed!
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: On dirait que ce puzzle de saut soit vraiment un cran au-dessus !

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: Mon dieu, that really is a long jump puzzle
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Mon dieu, il est vraiment long ce puzzle de saut.

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: Checkpoint... still not over...
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Un point de contrôle... c'est toujours pas fini...

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: Another checkpoint!\. With every step we're getting closer to that treasure!
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Encore une étape !\. À chaque pas, nous nous rapprochons de ce trésor !

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: Another milestone reached!
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Encore un point d'étape de franchi !

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: And that would be...\. our second checkpoint, right?
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Et ça serait notre...\. deuxième étape, pas vrai ?

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: At this point...\. I almost miss walking on water.
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Là...\. Ça me manquerait presque de pouvoir marcher sur l'eau.

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: By the Ancient's...\. it's still not over!
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Par les anciens...\. C'est toujours pas fini !

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: More stone hopping...
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Encore des rochers à sauter...

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: Aaaaaaand onward, I guess...
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Eeeeeet on continue...

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: WHY IS THAT JUMP PANEL NOT ACTIVATED?! SACREBLEU!!
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: POURQUOI EST-CE QUE CETTE PLAQUE DE SAUT N'EST PAS ACTIVÉE ?! SACREBLEU !!

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: Nope.\. It's off.\. Sadly...\. no jumping from here.
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Raté.\. C'est foutu.\. Malheureusement...\. pas moyen de sauter.

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: Oh no...\. I guess it's that ground switch...\. over there.
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Oh non...\. J'imagine que c'est cet interrupteur au sol...\. là-haut.

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: It seems we'll have to explore the surrounding first to proceed!
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Il semblerait que nous devons explorer les environs pour continuer !

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: Memorial Statue
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Statue Monument

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: Sir Blobikus Memorial
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Monument à Sir Étoilus

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: Surrounded by water...\. aren't you guys a bit nervous?
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Entouré d'eau...\. Ça ne vous rend pas un peu nerveux ?

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: It might look pleasant, but it's actually quite deadly here.
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Ça a l'air paisible, mais en fait c'est assez mortel ici.

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: Naturally shaped stone bridge.\. No, of course it doesn't make sense.\. Looks nice, though.
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Un pont de roche parfaitement naturel.\. Non, bien sûr ça n'a aucun sens.\. Mais c'est joli.

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: Those stones remind me a bit of those... \c[3]indecisive flowers\c[0] in Vermillion Wasteland!\. Remember those, Lea?
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Ces rochers me rappellent un peu ces... \c[3]fleurs indécises\c[0] à \v[area.arid.name] !\. Tu t'en souviens, Lea ?

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: This is just as narrow... but at least you don't have to repeat the whole thing when you fall into the water.
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: C'est tout aussi étroit... mais au moins il faut pas recommencer depuis le début si tu tombes dans l'eau.

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: Of course!\. The Ancients always reward those that explore ahead of time!\. It seems we missed a switch!
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Bien entendu !\. Les anciens récompensent toujours ceux qui explorent en avance !\. Il semblerait que nous ayons raté un interrupteur !

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: Ugh!\. Of course we had to hit another switch first.\. OF COURSE!
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Rah !\. Bien sûr il fallait qu'on touche un autre interrupteur avant.\. BIEN SÛR !

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: Oh, we didn't activate that jump panel yet?\. That sucks...
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Oh, on a pas encore activé cette plaque de saut ?\. Quelle misère...

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: Huh...\. Guess we can't go on here!\. I suppose we have to hit that switch first.
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Heu...\. J'imagine qu'on peut pas aller là-bas !\. Vraisemblablement il faut qu'on touche cet interrupteur avant.

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: Are we there yet?
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Est-ce qu'on est arrivé ?

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: Doesn't look like it ends here, huh?
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: On ne dirait pas que ça s'arrête ici, hein ?

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: As expected, the Ancients have prepared quite the formidable challenge!
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Comme on pouvait s'y attendre, les Anciens nous ont préparé un formidable défi !

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: Oui...\. It's going to be long.
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Oh, oui...\. Ça va être long.

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: And...\. more jumping!
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Et...\. encore des sauts !

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: Looks like I was right...
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: On dirait que j'avais raison...

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: Oh it's a checkpoint!\. How very nice of them.
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Oh, c'est un point d'étape !\. Comme c'est gentil de leur part.

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: Oh, that is a relief!\. I was starting to get stressed out about the thought of falling down.
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Oh, quel soulagement !\. Je commençais à stresser à l'idée de tomber en bas.

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: A checkpoint!\. The Ancients mean well with us!
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Un point d'étape !\. Les anciens ont pensé à nous !

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: Checkpoint! Nice!
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Un point d'étape ! Cool !

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: Hello, fellow Seeker!
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Bonjour, confrère \v[lore.title.seeker] !

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: Welcome to the Triblader corner!
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Bienvenue dans le Coin des Tribladers !

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: We wish you all the best on your journey.
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Nous vous souhaitons à tous un bon voyage.

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: Have a nice day!
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Passez une bonne journée dans ce paysage !

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: And make sure to enjoy the weather!
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Et profitez de la météo pleine de chaleur !

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: That's one of these long jump puzzles, isn't it?
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: C'est un de ces puzzles de saut à rallonge, c'est ça ?

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: Looks like we found an alternative route, more jumping ahead!
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: On dirait qu'on a trouvé un chemin alternatif, avec encore plus de sauts !

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: We've found a secret route!\. Let's see what the ancients have planned for us!
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Nous avons trouvé une route secrète !\. Voyons voir ce que les Anciens ont prévus pour nous !

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: I have this feeling we still have a lot more jumping to do...
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: J'ai le sentiment qu'on va avoir encore beaucoup de sauts à faire...

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: You think they can see us?
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Vous pensez qu'ils peuvent nous voir ?

extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.orig: Shhh!
extension/post-game/data/maps/beach/path.text: Chut !
